<pdfbody>
    <div style="height: 2.2cm;">
        &nbsp;
    </div>

    <table class="w-100">
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 4em;">Date</td>
            <td>: <%= @data[:letter_date] %></td>
            <td></td>
        </tr>
    </table><br>

    <table>
        <tr><td>FOMEMA Sdn Bhd</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Lot 49 & 51</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Jalan Kampung Pandan</td></tr>
        <tr><td>55100 Kuala Lumpur</td></tr>
    </table>
    <br>
    <table>
        <tr><td><%= @data[:employer_name].titleize %>
        <% @data[:employer_address].each do |address| %>
            <tr><td><%= address.titleize %></td></tr>
        <% end %>
    </table>

    <p class="paragraph-spacing">To whom it may concern,</p>

    <p class="paragraph-spacing letter-header-underline"><b>
        Renewal of Registration for Unsuitable Foreign Worker
    </b></p>

    <p class="paragraph-spacing" style="text-align: justify;">
        I have been informed of the current unsuitable status of the following foreign worker:
        <br>
        <table class="w-100" cellpadding="5" border="1">
            <tr><td style="width: 25%">Foreign Worker's Name</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @data[:worker_name].titleize %></td></tr>
            <tr><td style="width: 25%">Worker Code</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @data[:worker_code] %></td></tr>
            <tr><td style="width: 25%">Passport Number</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @data[:worker_passport] %></td></tr>
            <tr><td style="width: 25%">Country of Origin</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @data[:worker_country].titleize %></td></tr>
        </table>
    </p>
    <p class="paragraph-spacing" style="text-align: justify;">
       I understand that the foreign worker may need to undergo further investigations or
       auditing of the chest X-ray to ensure appropriate certification. I acknowledge
       that this process may exceed the normal 18 days period to complete the Foreign Workers' medical screening.
       I am also aware of the consequences, if the foreign worker is found unsuitable.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph-spacing">
       Thank you for your assistance.<br><br>
        Yours sincerely,<br><br><br>
        ............................................<br>
        <%= @data[:employer_name].titleize %>
    </p>
</pdfbody>

<style>
    pdfbody {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .w-100 {
        width: 100%;
    }

    .paragraph-spacing {
        padding-top: 0.5em;
    }

    .paragraph-double-spacing {
        padding-top: 1em;
    }

    .paragraph-triple-spacing {
        padding-top: 1.5em;
    }

    .paragraph-quad-spacing {
        padding-top: 2em;
    }

    .letter-header-underline {
        border-bottom: 2px solid black;
    }

    br {
        font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    td, tr {
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }
</style>